{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|2Co|2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","chapter":2,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","bookOrder":46,"chapter":2,"verse":1,"text":"In fact, I made up my mind about this: I would not come to you on another painful visit.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","bookOrder":46,"chapter":2,"verse":2,"text":"For if I cause you pain, then who will cheer me other than the one being hurt by me?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","bookOrder":46,"chapter":2,"verse":3,"text":"I wrote this very thing so that when I came I wouldn’t have pain from those who ought to give me joy, because I am confident about all of you that my joy will also be yours.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","bookOrder":46,"chapter":2,"verse":4,"text":"For I wrote to you with many tears out of an extremely troubled and anguished heart —not to cause you pain, but that you should know the abundant love I have for you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","bookOrder":46,"chapter":2,"verse":5,"text":"If anyone has caused pain, he has caused pain not so much to me but to some degree —not to exaggerate —to all of you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","bookOrder":46,"chapter":2,"verse":6,"text":"This punishment by the majority is sufficient for that person.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","bookOrder":46,"chapter":2,"verse":7,"text":"As a result, you should instead forgive and comfort him. Otherwise, he may be overwhelmed by excessive grief.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","bookOrder":46,"chapter":2,"verse":8,"text":"Therefore I urge you to reaffirm your love to him.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","bookOrder":46,"chapter":2,"verse":9,"text":"I wrote for this purpose: to test your character to see if you are obedient in everything.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","bookOrder":46,"chapter":2,"verse":10,"text":"Anyone you forgive, I do too. For what I have forgiven —if I have forgiven anything —it is for your benefit in the presence of Christ,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","bookOrder":46,"chapter":2,"verse":11,"text":"so that we may not be taken advantage of by Satan. For we are not ignorant of his schemes.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","bookOrder":46,"chapter":2,"verse":12,"text":"When I came to Troas to preach the gospel of Christ, even though the Lord opened a door for me,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","bookOrder":46,"chapter":2,"verse":13,"text":"I had no rest in my spirit because I did not find my brother Titus. Instead, I said good-bye to them and left for Macedonia.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","bookOrder":46,"chapter":2,"verse":14,"text":"But thanks be to God, who always leads us in Christ’s triumphal procession and through us spreads the aroma of the knowledge of him in every place.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","bookOrder":46,"chapter":2,"verse":15,"text":"For to God we are the fragrance of Christ among those who are being saved and among those who are perishing.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","bookOrder":46,"chapter":2,"verse":16,"text":"To some we are an aroma of death leading to death, but to others, an aroma of life leading to life. Who is adequate for these things?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","bookOrder":46,"chapter":2,"verse":17,"text":"For we do not market the word of God for profit like so many. On the contrary, we speak with sincerity in Christ, as from God and before God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Co","chapter":2,"paragraphStarts":[1,5,12,14],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":5,"text":"A Sinner Forgiven"},{"beforeVerse":12,"text":"A Trip to Macedonia"},{"beforeVerse":14,"text":"A Ministry of Life or Death"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"In fact, I made up my mind about this: I would not come to you on another painful visit. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit not again in sorrow to come to you"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit not again in sorrow to come to you"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For if I cause you pain, then who will cheer me other than the one being hurt by me? "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit the one pained"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Lit the one pained"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I wrote this very thing so that when I came I wouldn’t have pain from those who ought to give me joy, because I am confident "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:25","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" about all of you that my joy will also be yours. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Php 1:25","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For I wrote to you with many tears out of an extremely troubled and anguished heart —not to cause you pain, but that you should know the abundant love I have for you."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If anyone has caused pain, he has caused pain not so much to me but to some degree —not to exaggerate "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Th 3:8","book":"2Th","chapter":3,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" —to all of you. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Th 3:8","book":"2Th","chapter":3,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This punishment by the majority is sufficient for that person. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"As a result, you should instead forgive "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 6:12","book":"Mat","chapter":6,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and comfort him. Otherwise, he may be overwhelmed by excessive grief. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 6:12","book":"Mat","chapter":6,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore I urge you to reaffirm your love to him. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I wrote for this purpose: to test your character "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 5:4","book":"Rom","chapter":5,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" to see if you are obedient "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:8","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" in everything. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 5:4","book":"Rom","chapter":5,"verse":4},{"label":"Php 2:8","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Anyone you forgive, I do too. For what I have forgiven —if I have forgiven anything —it is for your benefit in the presence of Christ, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"so that we may not be taken advantage "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 12:17","book":"2Co","chapter":12,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" of by Satan. For we are not ignorant of his schemes."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Co 12:17","book":"2Co","chapter":12,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When I came to Troas "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:8","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" to preach the gospel of Christ, even though the Lord opened a door "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 4:3","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" for me, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 16:8","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":8},{"label":"Col 4:3","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I had no rest "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Th 1:7","book":"2Th","chapter":1,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" in my spirit because I did not find my brother Titus. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ti 1:4","book":"Tit","chapter":1,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" Instead, I said good-bye to them and left for Macedonia. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:9","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":9,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Th 1:7","book":"2Th","chapter":1,"verse":7},{"label":"Ti 1:4","book":"Tit","chapter":1,"verse":4},{"label":"Ac 16:9","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But thanks be to God, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:57","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":57,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" who always leads us in Christ’s triumphal procession and through us spreads the aroma of the knowledge of him in every place. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 17:3","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 4:8","book":"1Jn","chapter":4,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 15:57","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":57},{"label":"Jn 17:3","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":3},{"label":"1Jn 4:8","book":"1Jn","chapter":4,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For to God we are the fragrance "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 5:2","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 4:18","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Christ among those who are being saved "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 9:22","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":22,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:30","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":30,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:8","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":8,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" and among those who are perishing. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 6:27","book":"Jhn","chapter":6,"verse":27,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Eph 5:2","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":2},{"label":"Php 4:18","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":18},{"label":"Mt 9:22","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":22},{"label":"Ac 16:30","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":30},{"label":"Eph 2:8","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":8},{"label":"Jn 6:27","book":"Jhn","chapter":6,"verse":27}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"To some we are an aroma of death "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 10:21","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:51","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":51,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 3:10","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":10,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" leading to death, but to others, an aroma of life "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 5:12","book":"1Jn","chapter":5,"verse":12,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" leading to life. Who is adequate for these things? "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 10:21","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":21},{"label":"Jn 8:51","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":51},{"label":"Php 3:10","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":10},{"label":"1Jn 5:12","book":"1Jn","chapter":5,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Co:2:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For we do not market the word of God "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 12:36","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":36,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 4:14","book":"Mrk","chapter":4,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 6:47","book":"Luk","chapter":6,"verse":47,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 8:21","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":21,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:1","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 2:22","book":"Jhn","chapter":2,"verse":22,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 18:32","book":"Jhn","chapter":18,"verse":32,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 17:11","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":11,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 2:15","book":"2Ti","chapter":2,"verse":15,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 4:12","book":"Heb","chapter":4,"verse":12,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"text","text":" for profit like so many. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read like the rest"},{"kind":"text","text":" On the contrary, we speak with sincerity in Christ, as from God and before God."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 12:36","book":"Mat","chapter":12,"verse":36},{"label":"Mk 4:14","book":"Mrk","chapter":4,"verse":14},{"label":"Lk 6:47","book":"Luk","chapter":6,"verse":47},{"label":"Lk 8:21","book":"Luk","chapter":8,"verse":21},{"label":"Jn 1:1","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"Jn 2:22","book":"Jhn","chapter":2,"verse":22},{"label":"Jn 18:32","book":"Jhn","chapter":18,"verse":32},{"label":"Ac 17:11","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":11},{"label":"2Tm 2:15","book":"2Ti","chapter":2,"verse":15},{"label":"Heb 4:12","book":"Heb","chapter":4,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read like the rest"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783099541125}